title: Friday Feast #92Noon!
description: Reaction to the first round of the NFL Draft! Hear a post-draft chat with HC Mike Zimmer from Thursday night, Sinykin explains the Packers' Jordan Love selection, GM Rick Spielman, new Vikings rookie Justin Jefferson, and Chad Greenway is on the hotline for a couple segments as well!
